HEADWORD: Adriatic
<hw>A`dri*at"ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Adriaticus</ets>, <ets>Hadriaticus</ets>, fr. <ets>Adria</ets> or
<ets>Hadria</ets>, a town of the Veneti.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to
a sea so named, the northwestern part of which is known as the Gulf of
Venice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

